Redux
Redux is a predicatable state container for JavaScript apps.
It can be used with React, Angular, Vue or JS.
Redux is a library for JS applications.

* Reudx is a state container
. Redux stores the state of your applications.
. Consider a React app-state of a component.
. State of an app is the state represented by all the individual compoenets of that app.
. Redux will store and manage the application state.






